sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 1

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
Are you ready to build thunderous arms? This session is all about adding size and carving out definition.


Make sure your tempo is on point and lock in your form with the exercise tutorial to max your gains.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Prepare your arms for the heavy lifting to come.

exercises.title: Dumbbell incline bicep curl (25% lifting weight)
Dumbbell incline bicep curl (50% lifting weight)
Dumbbell incline bicep curl (75% lifting weight)

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Grab the dumbbells to define and pump up your arms.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Brace your core for stability as you rock your upper and lower arms.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: The equipment change up will keep your triceps working hard.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Now hit the cable machine to refine and define your triceps.
